snippet.title: The Tavern - 12 Minutes of Gameplay
snippet.description:
"The Tavern" is the first game from Moral Anxiety Studio. It stands between an interactive RPG and a complex, immersive Visual Novel. Take a look and don't be surprised if you're going to start thinking about choices you would like to make!

Coming out soon!

Our website: http://www.moralanxietystudio.com/
Find us on Tweeter: https://twitter.com/MoralAnxiety
Or on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/MoralAnxiety/

Music by Kevin MacLeod. : )
